title: Parts and Labor
description: Serves meat, veg options available. A vegan double cheeseburger made with a black bean patty, Daiya, and Vegenaise is offered as a $10 deal. It also comes with a side and either a shot or a beer for that price. A progressive hip open air bar with large tables and some communal sitting areas. Very industrial interior with a comfy feel. Free Wi-Fi. If you use the ATM on site, you get a free shot when you show them your receipt. Free parking in back.
